{"id":619596,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/10/【搞个大新闻】都这么搞-还有能播的比赛吗？/","date":"2019-10-10T08:32:31Z","modified":"2019-10-10T08:33:09Z","title":"【搞个大新闻】都这么搞 今后还有能播的比赛吗？","content":"<p>近日，中国全面封杀NBA火箭队事件仍在持续发酵：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>10月7日，NBA向北京的“<a href=\"https://sports.sina.com.cn/basketball/nba/2019-10-07/doc-iicezuev0528785.shtml\">道歉声明</a>”受到了部分美国政要和民众的谴责。</li>\n<li>10月8日，央视体育频道宣布暂停NBA赛事转播。</li>\n<li>10月9日，“中年粉红”宣称<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/10/%e3%80%90%e4%bc%97%e4%ba%ba%e6%8e%a8%e3%80%91%e8%ae%a9%e7%81%ab%e7%ae%ad%e9%98%9f%e9%99%b7%e5%85%a5%e4%ba%ba%e6%b0%91%e6%88%98%e4%ba%89%e7%9a%84%e6%b5%b7%e6%b4%8b/\">“让火箭队陷入人民战争的海洋”</a>&#8230;..</li>\n<li>10月9日晚，NBA中国赛上海站路灯宣传牌开始作业拆除。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>10月9日起，陆续有支持香港反送中运动的美国民众在NBA现场，他们身着“光复香港 时代革命”的T恤，并举出“SOUTH PARK WAS RIGHT”、“SHAME ON NBA”、“FREE HONGKONG”、“GOOGLE UYGHURS”等横幅。</p>\n<p><iframe title=\"&#039;Google Uighurs&#039; protest sign confiscated at basketball game\" width=\"1080\" height=\"810\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/vid4pMzaXp8?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p>有中文推友调侃称，倘若此类现场抗议形成规模，不光NBA，可能其他体育赛事中国媒体也难以实况转播了。</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Just had our “Free Hong Kong” sign confiscated at Capitol One Arena at the Wizards game against the Guangzhou Long Lions. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/FreeHongKong?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#FreeHongKong</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/NBA?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#NBA</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Censorship?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#Censorship</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/on1O4QdBUi\">pic.twitter.com/on1O4QdBUi</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Jon Schweppe (@JonSchweppe) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/JonSchweppe/status/1182070459355009027?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">October 9, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">The moment Sam Wachs and his wife are escorted out of the <a href=\"https://twitter.com/sixers?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@sixers</a> preseason game against a Chinese basketball team for yelling “Free Hong Kong.” <a href=\"https://twitter.com/6abc?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@6abc</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/3HlZxKXDzs\">pic.twitter.com/3HlZxKXDzs</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Christie Ileto (@Christie_Ileto) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Christie_Ileto/status/1181779722243575809?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">October 9, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">So far we are allowed our “Google Uyghurs” sign. They seemed annoyed with it. <a href=\"https://t.co/cMMu4ns8Nd\">pic.twitter.com/cMMu4ns8Nd</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Jon Schweppe (@JonSchweppe) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/JonSchweppe/status/1182074230705401862?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">October 9, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Honored to stand with friends tonight defending free speech in <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/America?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#America</a>, standing in solidarity with <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/HongKong?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#HongKong</a>, and speaking out against <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/CCP?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#CCP</a> bullying and the <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/NBA?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#NBA</a>’s embarrassing behavior. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/freedomhouse?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@freedomhouse</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hkdc_us?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@hkdc_us</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/8rKLmh4D9m\">https://t.co/8rKLmh4D9m</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/xxuhSW5mem\">pic.twitter.com/xxuhSW5mem</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Annie Boyajian (@AnnieBoyajian) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/AnnieBoyajian/status/1182071672481996800?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">October 9, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">美国NBA球迷发起众筹订做支持香港的黑色T恤，以2万美元为目标，结果两天收到4万3千美元，足以订做两万件T恤。这些T恤将在10月22日在洛杉矶Staples体育场举行的NBA赛季第一场比赛发给全体观众穿。看来墙内不仅是赛前赛，以后的比赛也都不能转播了。 <a href=\"https://t.co/Xvqz9v3i4Z\">pic.twitter.com/Xvqz9v3i4Z</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 方舟子 (@fangshimin) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/fangshimin/status/1182191363925741568?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">October 10, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">NBA spectators show support for HK protesters<br />Source: RTHK news<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/StandWithHongKong?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#StandWithHongKong</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/FreeHongKong?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#FreeHongKong</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/antichinazi?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#antichinazi</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/uvUotXfokq\">pic.twitter.com/uvUotXfokq</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Heidi 🇭🇰 (@heidikooooo) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/heidikooooo/status/1182188903463153664?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">October 10, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">10月9日晚华盛顿奇才队和广州龙狮队在美国首都华盛顿举行比赛前，香港支持者在球场外发放写着”光复香港 时代革命“的T恤，一些球迷拿到后立刻穿上进去看比赛。一些人举着”NBA耻辱“等标语口号。<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#香港</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/NBA?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#NBA</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/mJ8Fu7Enml\">pic.twitter.com/mJ8Fu7Enml</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 美国之音中文网 (@VOAChinese) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/VOAChinese/status/1182135180816875521?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">October 10, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n","author":974,"categories":[18271,38908,38923,38934,38955],"tags":[39086,38564,32985,39087,39088,8712]}